--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Tutorial_Stage01_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.Localization::UnityEngine.Localization.Tables.StringTable
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9e8e649b95611ab4f8923a645fe74ad3, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 32440283136
    m_Localized: Congratulations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226176
    m_Localized: You have been selected as one of our lucky test subjects.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226177
    m_Localized: First, allow me to explain your objective.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226178
    m_Localized: Your first objective is to escape this section.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226179
    m_Localized: The place blocked by those cardboard boxes
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226180
    m_Localized: is the gate to the next section.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226181
    m_Localized: Obstacles blocking a gate must be destroyed with bombs.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226182
    m_Localized: For now, move over to the bomb.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226183
    m_Localized: Use the WASD keys to move.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226184
    m_Localized: Now, go ahead and try moving around.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226185
    m_Localized: Excellent!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226186
    m_Localized: 'A historic first for humankind: the first step of a mouse walking
      on two legs!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226187
    m_Localized: Let us aim even higher.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226188
    m_Localized: Your next goal is to get over that ledge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226189
    m_Localized: Press the Space key to jump over it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226190
    m_Localized: Excellent!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226191
    m_Localized: The world's first bipedal jumping mouse has been born! Another achievement
      to be proud of.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226192
    m_Localized: Make good use of jumping and proceed farther ahead.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226193
    m_Localized: Now, let us use a little wisdom.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226194
    m_Localized: With your current jump height, you can only clear ledges up to 2.5
      blocks high.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226195
    m_Localized: However, the ledge in front of you is 3 blocks high.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226196
    m_Localized: That is a problem... but do not worry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226197
    m_Localized: There is a cushion on your right.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32482226198
    m_Localized: You can carry this cushion and place it wherever you like.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420480
    m_Localized: Oh! With this, it looks like you can get over the ledge.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420481
    m_Localized: First, stand in front of the cushion
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420482
    m_Localized: and press the E key to pick it up.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420483
    m_Localized: Excellent!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420484
    m_Localized: Next, while holding the cushion, move in front of the ledge
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420485
    m_Localized: and press the E key again to place it down.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420486
    m_Localized: 'Note: Holding the E key will throw it. To avoid mistakes here,
      a quick press is recommended.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420487
    m_Localized: There is no substitute for practice. Go ahead and try it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420488
    m_Localized: Excellent!!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420489
    m_Localized: With this, you have evolved into the world's first bipedal jumping
      intelligent mouse!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420490
    m_Localized: A feat worthy of history. Thank you for such wonderful experimental
      results!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420491
    m_Localized: We would like to head for the bomb now, but it is actually a little
      far away...
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420492
    m_Localized: Traveling on foot may take some time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420493
    m_Localized: In situations like that, hold the Shift key to run.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420494
    m_Localized: Please make good use of it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420495
    m_Localized: Incidentally, throwing an object while running gives it a little
      extra distance.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420496
    m_Localized: At last, you are in front of the bomb. From here on, it is a race
      against time!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420497
    m_Localized: However, bombs must be handled with caution.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420498
    m_Localized: 'As you can see, bombs behave like this:'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420499
    m_Localized: When you pick up a bomb, its timer starts.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420500
    m_Localized: Hold the E key to charge, then throw.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420501
    m_Localized: The longer you hold it, the farther it will fly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420502
    m_Localized: Now, try throwing the bomb into the gate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420503
    m_Localized: If you have time, touch the star-shaped object while the bomb is
      lit to aim for a bonus.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420504
    m_Localized: If you fail, hold the R key to try again.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420505
    m_Localized: 'Quick press: Reload to the bomb. Long press: Reset from the start
      of the stage.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420506
    m_Localized: That concludes the tutorial. I wish you the best of luck!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32486420507
    m_Localized: May fortune be on your side.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
